{"tid":2023513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1963年曼德拉叛國罪入獄；2018年天琦暴動罪入獄","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T06:37:24.000Z","uid":275160,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"625838a5610165bc2a95cf2e12121e899ea5628d","tid":2023513,"uid":275160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日南非，明日香港。</span><br />\n<br />\n1943年曼德拉成立非國大青年聯盟<br />\n（本民前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n推行反種族隔離大罷工<br />\n（和理非行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n當時非國政府的回應是實施大規模拘捕<br />\n1953年，《公共安全法》以推出戒嚴令<br />\n(大圍捕、23條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n1960年，泛非大組織搞反通行證運動，上街示威遊行<br />\n（街頭勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n警方曾向群眾開火，造成<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沙佩維爾大屠殺</span></strong></span><br />\n (梓樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n1961年，創立了「民族之矛」武裝組織，採取「游擊戰和恐怖主義行動」<br />\n破壞行動包括在夜深無人時炸毀軍事設施、發電站、電話線路和運輸系統<br />\n（最後係武裝化）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歷史總是重複。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭，你提出曼德拉叫香港人學習，我地一定會學到底。<br />\n中國終有日會支爆，香港人會好似非國人重建南非咁，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重光香港</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，送上攬炒巴既名言：<br />\n<br />\n「攬炒，唔係Burnism，係 Phoenixism，係鳳凰重生 嘅必經過程。香港人，再無同中共妥協嘅空間。<br />\n<br />\n但願從此人人覺醒，再無大眾、本土、泛民之分。<br />\n<br />\n但願我地告別犬儒，告別投降，告別內鬥，從此只有重光派，為煲底之約奮戰。<br />\n <br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵。<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn, you burn with us.」"},{"pid":"d4c5e9147e0e0de0e5689e89954355b05199cfa7","tid":2023513,"uid":64138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4993d745b29caf1bda6ed933fabbb508a881065c","tid":2023513,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"真孟德拉：Sometimes, it falls upon a generation to be great<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2023518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2023518</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"891d8177b80c97fe2b2067cfb26d7eb0798ebb4d","tid":2023513,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ae5ace5d7bea78d613c762d21d5cc8a94d1dc9","tid":2023513,"uid":275160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4993d745b29caf1bda6ed933fabbb508a881065c","tid":2023513,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"真孟德拉：Sometimes, it falls upon a generation to be great<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2023518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2023518</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:19:25.000Z","msg":"明明孟德拉先係革命軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭其心可居"},{"pid":"d71adb6d463b8825063f03712f9051db994ec430","tid":2023513,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea513820953b362328cd19e5632e440bfab0b1a7","tid":2023513,"uid":275160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4c5e9147e0e0de0e5689e89954355b05199cf